data.description: Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a ready-to-move-in, 3-bed 2-bath home on 5+ private acres in Cle Elum's recreational paradise. This thoughtfully designed home features an open floor plan, ideal for entertaining friends, an upgraded kitchen with new cabinets, all new appliances, new plank flooring, new front deck, new heat pump, new wood stove. Start your mornings with a cup of coffee and breathtaking views! Bring RV, snowmobiles, snow skis, fishing poles, and ATVs! With the Cascade Mountains as your backdrop, you can indulge in all four seasons of outdoor fun! Located just an hour east of Seattle and minutes from Snoqualmie Pass and Cle Elum!
